strings: <voice_0x01001D21><se_high>media princess: I still can't believe you're King Clavius' grandson.
<voice_0x01001D22><se_high>media princess: Are you a cousin of Prince Charming?
<voice_0x01001D24><se_high>media princess: ......I'm very sorry. I don't need to talk, make up your mind now, there's nothing we can do
<voice_0x01001D27><se_high>media princess: Monk, do you think this little mouse is Chen Mu?
<voice_0x01001D29><se_high>media princess: Many years ago we met in the forest. Maggie took me over to her place.
<voice_0x01001D2A><se_high>media princess: And Chin Mue was still looking at you and pulled out the pockets of her coat. this is so amazing!
